(en) The Sisters Rynning again, 7 July 1965

In the foreground, two women are seen at a café table with postcards and pencils in their hands. They are clothed crocheted longcofts and short-cut hairstyles. A further café is visible in the round - https://www.europeana.eu/item/916121/S_OLM_photo_OLM_2012_8_1860. (en) Örebro Kuriren. Örebro läns museum - https://digitaltmuseum.se/021016187036.
